holders = conversationIds.map(() => \'?\').join(\',\');\n  const msgResults = aw
ait this.dataSource.query(\n    `\n    SELECT m.* FROM messages m\n    INNER JOI
N (\n      SELECT conversation_id, MAX(sequence_id) as max_seq\n      FROM messa
ges\n      WHERE conversation_id IN (${placeholders})\n      GROUP BY conversati
on_id\n    ) latest ON m.conversation_id = latest.conversation_id AND m.sequence
_id = latest.max_seq\n  `,\n    conversationIds,\n  );\n  ```\n- **依据**: `docs
